<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='203195' id='t-203195'>than displaying their idiocy?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='205746' id='t-205746'>So, let's see.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='207535' id='t-207535'>From user name Liquidsore29 --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='210259' id='t-210259'>interesting user names we have here—</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='212268' id='t-212268'>&amp;quot;Disgusting liberal moms making their sons gay.&amp;quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='218048' id='t-218048'>Liquidsore29, really? Really? Okay.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='220803' id='t-220803'>How about from Whiteboy77AGS:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='224643' id='t-224643'>&quot;People always need something
