<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='228792' id='t-228792'>From Jeffrey Gutierrez:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='231082' id='t-231082'>&amp;quot;OMG, shut up. You just want money and attention.&amp;quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:05
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='234098' id='t-234098'>So it was comments like these</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='236371' id='t-236371'>that really discouraged me from
